Use plugin system:

- use own config, language file, javascript file and css file and stored it local
- system starting index.php, you need use include() for config
- system give you:
     $SYS_PLUGINS_DIR - plugin directory
     example: $fl=$SYS_PLUGINS_DIR."myplugin/some.css"; include($fl);
- use variable to test plugin:
     $MYPLUGIN=true; function myplugin(); - in plugin file
     if (isset($MYPLUGIN)){ myplugin();}  - place to use it
